    "body": "@samouss, I spent way too much time trying to figure this out -- this should have been in the documentation. Nearly 3 years ago (https://blog.algolia.com/geo-search-on-steroid/), Algolia touted the ability to pass an array of locations, so why is it not part of the widget?",
