    "body": "You are right it should be in the documentation. We have added it in [the requirements section](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/geoSearch.html#requirements) of the widget. We know that we don't cover all the use cases. But this is the first version of the geo widget. We are gathering feedback about his usage, it will help us to implement the proper features in a next version.",
