  {
    "author_association": "CONTRIBUTOR",
    "body": "For the moment the only way to get a reference of the map instance is through [the events listeners on the markers](https://community.algolia.com/instantsearch.js/v2/widgets/geoSearch.html#struct-BuiltInMarkerOptions). The instance is provided as argument of the listener. We dot not provide a hook to access the instance directly otherwise. Could you give us a bit more context about your use case? It will help to better understand the issue and to find a possible solution. Thanks!",
